TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
Select 'SELECT /*+ index('|| Table_Name ||') */ ''' || Table_Name || ''' ,FILENAME, RECORDNUMBER, ' || REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(UPPER(replace( rk.FieldNameList , ',' , '||''~''||' )),'UPPER(',''),'LOWER(',''),')','') || ',' || Column_Name || ', ''' || Column_Name ||''''||',' ||fv.Conditionid ||','||fv.ISWARNINGONLY|| ' FROM ' || Table_Name || ' WHERE FILENAME = ''' || '$$filename' || ''' ' || ' AND nvl(IS_FILTERED,0)=0 '
From ALL_TAB_COLUMNS atc, TELS_CORE_FIELDVALIDATION fv, TELS_CORE_RECORDKEY rk Where substr(atc.Owner,1,4) = substr(User,1,4) And atc.Table_Name = '$$prestage_tablename' And atc.Column_Name Not in ('FILENAME','RECORDNUMBER') And fv.TableName = atc.Table_Name And fv.FieldName = atc.Column_Name And rk.TableName(+) = fv.TableName And rk.IsPrimaryRecordKey = 1 Order By Column_ID, FV.CONDITIONID DESC

TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DATE_VALUE AS "DATE_VALUE" , PERIOD_NAME AS "PERIOD_NAME" , DATE_TYPE AS "DATE_TYPE" FROM ( WITH INDEX_LIST AS ( SELECT MD.RULEELEMENTSEQ AS "RULEELEMENTSEQ" , MD.DIMENSIONSLOT AS "DIMENSION_NUMBER" , MD.NAME AS "DIMENSION_NAME" , MI.ORDINAL AS "INDEX_NUMBER" , NVL(MI.MINSTRING, TO_CHAR(MI.MINVALUE)) AS "INDEX_NAME" , MI.EFFECTIVESTARTDATE AS "INDEX_START_DATE" , MI.EFFECTIVEENDDATE AS "INDEX_END_DATE" FROM CS_MDLTDIMENSION MD JOIN CS_MDLTINDEX MI ON MI.RULEELEMENTSEQ = MD.RULEELEMENTSEQ AND MI.DIMENSIONSEQ = MD.DIMENSIONSEQ AND MI.REMOVEDATE = MD.REMOVEDATE AND MI.EFFECTIVESTARTDATE < MD.EFFECTIVEENDDATE AND MI.EFFECTIVEENDDATE > MD.EFFECTIVESTARTDATE WHERE (1=1) AND MD.REMOVEDATE = TO_DATE('01/01/2200', 'DD/MM/YYYY') ) SELECT MC.DATEVALUE AS "DATE_VALUE" , I1.INDEX_NAME AS "PERIOD_NAME" , I2.INDEX_NAME AS "DATE_TYPE" FROM CS_RELATIONALMDLT RM JOIN CS_MDLTCELL MC ON MC.MDLTSEQ = RM.RULEELEMENTSEQ AND MC.REMOVEDATE = RM.REMOVEDATE AND MC.EFFECTIVESTARTDATE < RM.EFFECTIVEENDDATE AND MC.EFFECTIVEENDDATE > RM.EFFECTIVESTARTDATE JOIN INDEX_LIST I1 ON I1.DIMENSION_NUMBER = 0 AND I1.RULEELEMENTSEQ = RM.RULEELEMENTSEQ AND I1.INDEX_NUMBER = MC.DIM0INDEX AND I1.INDEX_START_DATE < MC.EFFECTIVEENDDATE AND I1.INDEX_END_DATE > MC.EFFECTIVESTARTDATE JOIN INDEX_LIST I2 ON I2.DIMENSION_NUMBER = 1 AND I2.RULEELEMENTSEQ = RM.RULEELEMENTSEQ AND I2.INDEX_NUMBER = MC.DIM1INDEX AND I2.INDEX_START_DATE < MC.EFFECTIVEENDDATE AND I2.INDEX_END_DATE > MC.EFFECTIVESTARTDATE WHERE (1=1) AND RM.REMOVEDATE = TO_DATE('01/01/2200', 'DD/MM/YYYY') AND RM.NAME = 'LT_Payment_Date' AND RM.ISLAST = 1 )
